                    </div>
                    <span>The title should be How to use the I Ching if you have experience with the I Ching.  It is a nice book if you use it as a supplement to other books.  There are much better books than this one if you want an easy to use guide to the I Ching.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Amazing - Focus, ask, read, and learn</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
